baking right beside you!

34
00:01:48,251 --> 00:01:50,459
Oh, jeez! I didn't know we had company!

35
00:01:50,545 --> 00:01:51,752
Hey. Hi, I'm Dave.

36
00:01:51,838 --> 00:01:53,191
