45
00:02:11,233 --> 00:02:12,349
- Oh.
- Hey...

46
00:02:13,276 --> 00:02:16,019
I can't believe
I have to wait in line to see my own sister.

47
00:02:16,113 --> 00:02:20,357
I have never waited in any kind of
formation before, let alone a line.

48
00:02:20,492 --> 00:02:24,202
- Wow, is this whole room just her work?
- Don't be fooled, Chidi.

49
00:02:24,287 --> 00:02:25,698
Kamilah is a charlatan.

50
