74
00:03:27,851 --> 00:03:28,809
Cheddar or Swiss?

75
00:03:28,810 --> 00:03:31,456
Oh, no, I don't want an omelette.
I just came for a quick sisterly chat.

76
00:03:32,647 --> 00:03:35,890
