92
00:04:24,783 --> 00:04:27,150
Seven shots of Seagram's Seven,
in seven minutes.

93
00:04:27,327 --> 00:04:28,784
It's Diana's morning drink.

94
00:04:28,912 --> 00:04:30,995
Oh, that's right,
it was very early in the morning!

95
00:04:31,081 --> 00:04:33,309
Well, this little spitfire finds out

96
00:04:33,333 --> 00:04:35,916
