102
00:04:48,765 --> 00:04:49,881
Cute!

103
00:04:50,308 --> 00:04:51,869
So how did you and Eleanor become friends?

104
00:04:51,893 --> 00:04:53,475
Well, let's just say that we...

105
00:04:53,979 --> 00:04:57,063
