106
00:04:57,107 --> 00:04:58,473
Oh!

107
00:04:58,567 --> 00:05:00,775
What a fun way to say a normal thing, right?

108
00:05:00,902 --> 00:05:04,020
Well, I've gotta go get ready,
today is PTA elections

109
00:05:04,072 --> 00:05:05,279
