Is that all, then?

136
00:06:32,118 --> 00:06:33,118
Well...

137
00:06:38,333 --> 00:06:39,333
Oh!

138
00:06:45,298 --> 00:06:46,298
Urgh!

139
00:06:47,884 --> 00:06:49,216
Check out what Dave gave me.

140
00:06:49,719 --> 00:06:54,965
Plans for a Subaru dealership-slash-burlesque
club he's designing in Reno!

141
00:06:55,558 --> 00:06:57,345
Man, Nevada's a mess!

142
