179
00:08:45,126 --> 00:08:47,994
which will hinder any air
from getting into her lungs.

180
00:08:48,213 --> 00:08:49,795
Can I talk to her?

181
00:08:49,881 --> 00:08:52,498
Maybe we should try a little
third-party mediation.

182
00:08:55,553 --> 00:08:59,092
Uh, hi. I'm Tahani's friend, Chidi.

183
00:08:59,349 --> 00:09:01,682
Chidi is an Igbo word
that means "God exists."

184
00:09:02,560 --> 00:09:04,051
That's right. Sorry...

185
00:09:04,145 --> 00:09:06,888
