Stand up, sweetheart!

215
00:10:44,954 --> 00:10:47,321
Well, it was the first Hooters
ever made out of brick.

216
00:10:47,415 --> 00:10:49,873
- Sort of inspired by Monticello.
- Hey, mark.

217
00:10:49,918 --> 00:10:52,001
- Oh, nope, it's Dave.
- I know your name.

218
00:10:52,170 --> 00:10:53,706
